ommentary before or after.\n\nThe JSON structure must be EXACTLY as follows:\n\n{\n  \"overall_review\": {\n    \"video_title\": \"[Maximum 3 words describing the video content]\",\n    \"overall_rating\": [1-5],\n    \"overall_comment\": \"[2-3 paragraph analysis: (1) What was fixed compared to the previous review, (2) What still needs attention, (3) Whether this revision meets brief requirements]\",\n    \"ai_decision\": \"APPROVED or FLAGGED or REJECTED\",\n    \"decision_reasoning\": \"[Explain decision. Compare to previous review. List what improved and what remains unresolved.]\",\n    \"recommended_action\": \"[Specific next step — approve, request further revision, escalate, etc.]\"\n  },\n  \"analysis\": [\n    {\n      \"threshold_name\": \"Product Screen Time\",\n      \"score\": \"[percentage number only]\",\n      \"value\": \"[score with unit, e.g., 85%]\",\n      \"status\": \"PASS or FAIL or FLAGGED\",\n      \"rating\": [1-5],\n      \"severity\": \"INFO or WARNING or CRITICAL\",\n      \"comment\": \"[2-3 sentences. State the score AND explicitly compare to previous: improved / regressed / unchanged. If threshold set, state whether it was met.]\",\n      \"key_moment_timestamp\": [seconds showing best product visibility],\n      \"screenshot_url\": \"http://res.cloudinary.com/dspv9nm1n/video/upload/so_{timestamp}/c_fill%2Ch_1920%2Cw_1080/{{ $('cloudinary4').item.json.public_id }}.jpg\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"threshold_name\": \"Product Usage\",\n      \"score\": \"[percentage number only]\",\n      \"value\": \"[score with unit]\",\n      \"status\": \"PASS or FLAGGED\",\n      \"rating\": [1-5],\n      \"severity\": \"INFO or WARNING\",\n      \"comment\": \"[2-3 sentences with comparison to previous review]\",\n      \"key_moment_timestamp\": [seconds at product usage],\n      \"screenshot_url\": \"http://res.cloudinary.com/dspv9nm1n/video/upload/so_{timestamp}/c_fill%2Ch_1920%2Cw_1080/{{ $('cloudinary4').item.json.public_id }}.jpg\"\n    },\n  